        Construct a Builder for a RawIndexQuery with a range.

        Note that your index name should not include the Riak _int or _bin extension as these are supplied by the type.

        Parameters:
        namespace - The namespace in Riak to query.
        indexName - The index name in Riak to query.
        type - The Riak index type.
        start - The start of the 2i range.
        end - The end of the 2i range.
